h3#treeview Tree View

p
    | Use
    code Subtle.TreeView(object, nodes, params)
    |  to display a tree view

p.
    The nodes argument is a list with all the nodes in the tree (see the example).

//
h4 Example

div#treeview_div(style="width:100%;")

script.
    var nodes = [
        { path: 'A/B/X' },
        { path: 'A/B/Y' },
        { path: 'A/C/X' },
        { path: 'A/C/Z' },
        { path: 'A/W' },
    ];
    var treeview = new Subtle.TreeView("treeview_div", nodes, {
        show_arrows: true,
        show_checkboxes: true
    })


